from collections import Counter
from operator import itemgetter

def letter_frequency(text: str) -> list[tuple[str, int]]:
    filtered_text = (c for c in text.lower() if c.isalpha())
    frequency_count = Counter(filtered_text)
    items = frequency_count.items()
    sorted_items = sorted(sorted(items, key=itemgetter(0)), key=itemgetter(1), reverse=False)
    return sorted_items
